      <div class="row ">
        <div class="">
            <h3 class="h2">Shalom and Welcome!</h2>
            <div class="border border-3 border-dark w-15 mb-4"></div>
            <p>I'm a programmer from NYC that has been obsessed with the internet and new media since 1994. I dropped out of college at 20 to work at a hedge fund and a few years later started my first company, <a href="https://www.designerpages.com">Designer Pages</a>.</p>
            <p>Around 2010 I started teaching people how to code, mentoring them, and connecting them with jobs and that snowballed into founding <a href="https://flatironschool.com">Flatiron School</a> as the Dean and Chief Product Officer. Just about 10 years later, Flatiron School has helped over 10,000 people transition their career into code. In October 2021, I joined <a href="https://revature.com">Revature</a> as the Chief Product Officer where I work on training platform, strategy, and pedagogy.</p>
            <p><strong>You can learn more about my career and work history on my <a href="https://work.avi.nyc">Worklog</a>.</strong></p>
            <p>I'm excited about college alternatives, real-time interactive media, personal coaching and automated accountability, Bitcoin. I would love to hear about what gets you going.</p>
            <h3 class="text-center text-muted font-sans-serif" style="font-size: 0.8rem">I'm legit, I've been in all these publications (and more)!</h3>
            <img src="images/logos.png" class="mx-auto d-block img-fluid" usemap="#press-map">

